  <mainContent><![CDATA[<h3>USP College was created in August 2017, following the merger of Seevic College and Palmer's College.</h3>
<p>One of the largest colleges locally, we employ over 1000 people across our Benfleet and Grays campus.</p>
<p><span>We value our staff and are committed to investing in them and their futures – offering competitive salaries, benefits and training packages.</span></p>
<p><span>This section is currently under development if you would like to find out more about the working at the college please email <a href="mailto:hradmin&amp;recruitment@uspcollege.ac.uk" title="HR">hradmin&amp;recruitment@uspcollege.ac.uk </a></span></p>]]></mainContent>
